#storage types

object storage:
 - S3 (object storage, scalablility, securit, availability, performance; hot and cold options)

File Storage:
 - EFS (fully managed, scalable storage in Amazon Cloud, not high performance enough for ML requirements)
 - FSx for windows (managed windows file system, not parallel like Lustre is)
 -FSx for Lustre (fast processing, parallel file system to reduce bottlenecks)

block storage:
 - EBS (cold EBS is more expensive than S3 glacier - less gor for for archiving)

backup :
 - AWS backup

data transfer:
 - AWS storage gateway, datasync, transfer family, snow family


